---
// InteractiveMap.astro
// A simplified representation of US locations where data centers have spurred rural prosperity
---

<div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-slate-200 p-8 lg:p-12 mb-20 relative overflow-hidden group/map" id="interactive-map">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 relative z-10">
        <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">A National Pattern of Success</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">From the Pacific Northwest to the Silicon Heartland, rural communities are leveraging data center infrastructure to secure their financial futures.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Map Container -->
    <div class="relative w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto aspect-[16/9] bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
        
        <!-- Abstract US Map using basic SVG shapes and paths for a stylistic look -->
        <svg viewBox="0 0 800 500" class="w-full h-full text-slate-200 opacity-60">
            <!-- Simplified US Outline -->
            <path fill="currentColor" d="M100 100 L300 50 L600 80 L750 150 L750 350 L600 450 L400 480 L300 400 L200 450 L50 350 L50 150 Z" />
            <!-- Grid overlay for tech feel -->
            <defs>
                <pattern id="grid" width="40" height="40" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                    <path d="M 40 0 L 0 0 0 40" fill="none" stroke="rgba(0,0,0,0.05)" stroke-width="1"/>
                </pattern>
            </defs>
            <path fill="url(#grid)" d="M100 100 L300 50 L600 80 L750 150 L750 350 L600 450 L400 480 L300 400 L200 450 L50 350 L50 150 Z" />
        </svg>

        <!-- Data Point: Quincy, WA -->
        <div class="absolute top-[20%] left-[15%] group/point cursor-pointer z-20">
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="absolute w-12 h-12 bg-pine-green/20 rounded-full animate-ping opacity-75"></div>
                <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-pine-green rounded-full shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(16,185,129,0.8)] border-2 border-white relative z-10"></div>
                <!-- Tooltip -->
                <div class="absolute bottom-full left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 mb-4 w-64 bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-2xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover/point:opacity-100 group-hover/point:visible transition-all duration-300 translate-y-2 group-hover/point:translate-y-0 pointer-events-none">
                    <div class="text-xs font-bold text-pine-green uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Microsoft</div>
                    <div class="text-lg font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-2">Quincy, WA</div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-slate-300">Funded a new high school, library, and hospital through massive property tax increases.</div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 rotate-45"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Data Point: Prineville, OR -->
        <div class="absolute top-[30%] left-[12%] group/point cursor-pointer z-20">
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="absolute w-12 h-12 bg-tech-blue/20 rounded-full animate-ping opacity-75" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;"></div>
                <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-tech-blue rounded-full shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(59,130,246,0.8)] border-2 border-white relative z-10"></div>
                <!-- Tooltip -->
                <div class="absolute bottom-full left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 mb-4 w-64 bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-2xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover/point:opacity-100 group-hover/point:visible transition-all duration-300 translate-y-2 group-hover/point:translate-y-0 pointer-events-none">
                    <div class="text-xs font-bold text-tech-blue uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Meta</div>
                    <div class="text-lg font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-2">Prineville, OR</div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-slate-300">Saved a declining timber town. Wages rose from lowest to highest in the state.</div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 rotate-45"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Data Point: New Albany, OH -->
        <div class="absolute top-[35%] right-[25%] group/point cursor-pointer z-20">
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="absolute w-12 h-12 bg-amber-500/20 rounded-full animate-ping opacity-75" style="animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
                <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-amber-500 rounded-full shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(245,158,11,0.8)] border-2 border-white relative z-10"></div>
                <!-- Tooltip -->
                <div class="absolute bottom-full left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 mb-4 w-64 bg-slate-900 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-2xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover/point:opacity-100 group-hover/point:visible transition-all duration-300 translate-y-2 group-hover/point:translate-y-0 pointer-events-none">
                    <div class="text-xs font-bold text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Amazon / Google / Meta</div>
                    <div class="text-lg font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-2">New Albany, OH</div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-slate-300">Created the 'Silicon Heartland'. Amazon alone added $1.4B to local GDP.</div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-slate-900 rotate-45"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Data Point: Bastrop, TX (The Future) -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-[25%] left-[45%] group/point cursor-pointer z-30">
            <div class="relative flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="absolute w-20 h-20 bg-slate-900/10 rounded-full animate-pulse opacity-100"></div>
                <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-slate-900 rounded-full shadow-lg border-4 border-white relative z-10 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
                </div>
                <!-- Tooltip -->
                <div class="absolute bottom-full left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 mb-4 w-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-tech-blue border border-tech-blue/30 rounded-xl p-4 shadow-2xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover/point:opacity-100 group-hover/point:visible transition-all duration-300 translate-y-2 group-hover/point:translate-y-0 pointer-events-none">
                    <div class="text-xs font-bold text-tech-blue uppercase tracking-widest mb-1 drop-shadow-sm">The Next Chapter</div>
                    <div class="text-xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-2">Bastrop County, TX</div>
                    <div class="text-sm text-blue-100 font-medium">Positioned to secure generational wealth, fully fund ISDs, and drastically lower residential property taxes.</div>
                    <div class="absolute -bottom-2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-4 h-4 bg-tech-blue rotate-45"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center mt-6 text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">
        Hover over locations to see community impacts.
    </div>
</div>
